window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Under the protection of the gods, a relaxed life with slimes in another world begins!</p> <p>One day, the life of middle-aged Japanese businessman Ryoma Takebayashi came to a rather sudden and disappointing end. Ryoma had never had a blessed life, but after his death, three great gods sought his cooperation and reincarnated him as a child in another world with swords and magic!</p>"; 
